snippet.title: Desert Falcon (Atari 7800)
snippet.description:
Desert Falcon for the Atari 7800 played on my s-video/composite modded 7800.  I'm not very good at the game, but I did make it through several stages.

If the colors look a little different to you, that's because I tweaked them on a few stages to be a little more appropriate, and because my capture card looks a bit different in a few portions of the color palette (mostly browns).
